Package: r2EO
Title: Create study areas, download EO data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Christian", "Devenish", email= "c.devenish@keele.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates study area polygons from existing sample points or polygons, and downloads remote sensed data from LPDAAC, including ASTER, STRTM digital elevation models, MODIS, Landsat and Sentinel data. 
